success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104vhx1665702714312.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/vhx1665702714312.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/vhx1665702714312.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"vhx1665702714312\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n       Snippet Library\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">A Snippet Library contains code Snippets that can copied and pasted into your code during development.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"vhx1665702714312__section_hld_tgv_mwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d747365e51\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"vhx1665702714312__p_d96590e1_d96591e1_d96592e1\">Snippet Libraries are automatically made available in the\n          <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Snippet</span> tab of the Resource Browser in the Write Script and Design\n        Layout worksheets.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"vhx1665702714312__section_ztf_5gv_mwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d747365e63\">Characteristics</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"vhx1665702714312__table_d10754e1_d10755e1_d10756e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"vhx1665702714312__table_d10754e1_d10755e1_d10756e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Characteristics</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"vhx1665702714312__table_d10754e1_d10755e1_d10756e1__entry__2\"></th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vhx1665702714312__table_d10754e1_d10755e1_d10756e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Icon:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vhx1665702714312__table_d10754e1_d10755e1_d10756e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\"><img alt=\"Icon\" class=\"image\" id=\"vhx1665702714312__image_esr_wgv_mwb\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/library_snippet.png?_LANG=enus\"/></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vhx1665702714312__table_d10754e1_d10755e1_d10756e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Object type code:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vhx1665702714312__table_d10754e1_d10755e1_d10756e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">libsnp</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vhx1665702714312__table_d10754e1_d10755e1_d10756e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Main Development Object?</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vhx1665702714312__table_d10754e1_d10755e1_d10756e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Yes</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vhx1665702714312__table_d10754e1_d10755e1_d10756e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Part of:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vhx1665702714312__table_d10754e1_d10755e1_d10756e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">—</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vhx1665702714312__table_d10754e1_d10755e1_d10756e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Contains:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vhx1665702714312__table_d10754e1_d10755e1_d10756e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jgi1665702550212.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jgi1665702550212.html\" title=\"A Property is a named, typed attribute of Development Object that defines a characteristic or behavior of the object. Each property has a descriptive name, a literal name, a data type, and a value. If no value is specified, a default value may be used.\">Property</a>, <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"vqc1665703032032.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vqc1665703032032.html\" title=\"A Snippet is a Development Object that defines a fragment of code or text that can be inserted into code.\">Snippet</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vhx1665702714312__table_d10754e1_d10755e1_d10756e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Generalization:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vhx1665702714312__table_d10754e1_d10755e1_d10756e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"srw1665702550375.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/srw1665702550375.html\" title=\"A Main Development Object is a Development Object that has no parent object, is maintained using a dedicated editor, and can be saved and exported as a single unit, with all its children.\">Main Development Object</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vhx1665702714312__table_d10754e1_d10755e1_d10756e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Specializations:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vhx1665702714312__table_d10754e1_d10755e1_d10756e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">—</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vhx1665702714312__table_d10754e1_d10755e1_d10756e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Compilation Output:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vhx1665702714312__table_d10754e1_d10755e1_d10756e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">—</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vhx1665702714312__table_d10754e1_d10755e1_d10756e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">URI format:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vhx1665702714312__table_d10754e1_d10755e1_d10756e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">libsnp:<var class=\"keyword varname\">LibraryName</var>\n</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"vhx1665702714312__section_rpr_xgv_mwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d747365e266\">Specialization</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"vhx1665702714312__p_d96599e1_d96600e1_d96601e1\">Snippet Library specializes Main Development Object and\n        Library in the following ways:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"vhx1665702714312__ul_hk5_ygv_mwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vhx1665702714312__li_d39296e1_d39297e1_d39298e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"vhx1665702714312__p_d96602e1_d96603e1_d96604e1\">It can only contain code fragments of any type.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3616512\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3616512\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Snippet Library Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 09, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Snippet Library A Snippet Library contains code Snippets that can copied and pasted into your code during development. Description Snippet Libraries are automatically made available in the Snippet tab of the Resource Browser in the Write Script and Design Layout worksheets. Characteristics Characteristics Icon: Object type code: libsnp Main Development Object? Yes Part of: — Contains: Property , Snippet Generalization: Main Development Object Specializations: — Compilation Output: — URI format: libsnp: LibraryName Specialization Snippet Library specializes Main Development Object and Library in the following ways: It can only contain code fragments of any type. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}